parameters.name: $SQ_gw_risk$
parameters.label: SQ_gw_risk
parameters.customQuery:
with policyDetails as (select distinct rowinsdt as gw_policydetail_row_strt_dt, PolicyKey ,
PolicyForm as form,
CarrierCd,
LineOfBusiness,
CASE
               WHEN "LineOfBusiness" IN ('Businessowners', 'CommercialUmbrella') THEN 26
               ELSE 25
           END AS policy_parent_dim_id,
ShellPolicyInd
From int_msgr.PolicyDetail P where P.ShellPolicyInd IS NULL )

SELECT 
'Guidewire' as datasource_name,
riskid as risk_key,
P."CarrierCd" || P."PolicyKey" || R."RiskID" AS policy_key_code,
'1' as policy_key_code_flag,
R.BlanketBasisInd AS blanket_policy_ind,
--COALESCE(P.form, 'Not Applicable') AS form,
COALESCE(R.RiskState, 'Not Applicable') AS risk_state,
CASE
    WHEN OccupancyCd IS NULL THEN 'Not Applicable'
    WHEN OccupancyCd = 'Secondary Residence' THEN 'Secondary/Seasonal'
    ELSE 'Primary/Non-seasonal'
END 
AS secondary_home_desc,
R.CovAPremium AS cov_a_premium,
R.CovCPremium AS cov_c_premium,
COALESCE(R.BuildingLimitDesc, 'Not Applicable') AS building_limits_group,
COALESCE(L."DisplayValue", '0') AS building_limits,
    CASE
        WHEN R.buildingstatus <> 'Deleted' THEN CAST(R."BuildingLimit" AS NUMERIC(8, 0))
        ELSE 0 END AS building_limit_amt,
    COALESCE(Band_1K,  'Not Applicable') AS building_limit_band_1k,
    COALESCE(Band_100K, 'Not Applicable') AS building_limit_band_100k,
    COALESCE(Band_500K, 'Not Applicable') AS building_limit_band_500k,
    CASE
        WHEN R."buildingstatus" <> 'Deleted' THEN CAST(R."ContentsLimit" AS NUMERIC(8, 0))
        ELSE 0
    END AS contents_limit,
    CASE
        WHEN R."buildingstatus" <> 'Deleted' THEN R."TotalInsuredValue"
        ELSE 0
    END  AS total_insured_value,
    COALESCE(R.IndividualRiskPremiumMod, 'Not Applicable') AS individual_risk_premium_mod,
    COALESCE(R.ExpenseMod, 'Not Applicable') AS expense_mod,
    COALESCE(R.AgeCreditAmt, 'Not Applicable') AS age_credit_amt,
    COALESCE(R.DUPCCreditAmt, 'Not Applicable') AS dupc_credit_amt,
    'Not Applicable' AS prc_credit,
    COALESCE(R.latitude, 'Not Applicable') AS latitude,
    COALESCE(R.longitude, 'Not Applicable') AS longitude,
    R.OptionalDedType AS wind_deductible_type,
    R.OptionalDed AS wind_deductible_amt,
    R.PerUnitDeductibleType AS per_unit_deductible_type,
    R.PerUnitDeductibleAmt AS per_unit_deductible_amt,
    CAST(LEFT("DistanceToShoreFeet", LENGTH("DistanceToShoreFeet") - 3) AS VARCHAR) AS distance_to_shore_feet,
    R.DistanceToShoreMile AS distance_to_shore_mile,
    CAST(LEFT("SIRCoastlineFeet", LENGTH("SIRCoastlineFeet") - 3) AS VARCHAR) AS sir_coastline_feet,
    CAST(R.SIRCoastlineMile AS VARCHAR) AS sir_coastline_mile,
    COALESCE(R.FloodZone, 'Not Applicable') AS flood_zone,
    COALESCE(R.Elevation, 'Not Applicable') AS elevation,
    COALESCE(R.BuildingClassCd, R.ContentsClassCd, 'Not Applicable') AS class_code,
    COALESCE(R.BuildingClassCd, 'Not Applicable') AS building_class_code,
    COALESCE(R.ContentsClassCd, 'Not Applicable') AS contents_class_code,
    COALESCE(R.ConstructionCd, 'Unknown Construction Type') AS construction_type,
    COALESCE(R.YearBuilt, 'Unknown Construction Year') AS construction_year,
    COALESCE(Y.display_value, 'Unknown Construction Year') AS construction_year_band,
    COALESCE(DL."DisplayValue", 'Unknown Limit') AS contents_limits_group,
    COALESCE(DL."DisplayValue", 'Unknown Limit') AS contents_limits,
	--coverage_desc
   
   COALESCE(R.LiabilityLimit, 'Other') AS liability_limit,
    COALESCE(R.CommercialLiabilityLimit, 'Other') AS commercial_liability_limit,
    R.WaterBackupLimit AS water_backup_limit,
    COALESCE(
    LTRIM(REPEAT('0', 3 - LENGTH(R."NumberOfApartment"))) || R."NumberOfApartment",
    "NumberOfApartmentsCondo",
    'Not Applicable'
) AS number_of_apartments,
    CASE
        WHEN R."NumberofFamilies" IS NOT NULL THEN
            LTRIM(REPEAT('0', 2 - LENGTH(R."NumberofFamilies"))) || R."NumberofFamilies"
        ELSE 'Other'		END	AS number_of_families,
    COALESCE(O."Display_OccupancyDesc", 'Not Applicable') AS occupancy,
	COALESCE(
    LTRIM(REPEAT('0', 2 - LENGTH(R."ProtectionClass"))) || R."ProtectionClass",
    'Not Applicable'
) AS protection_class,
    COALESCE(R.SprinklerCd, 'Not Applicable') AS sprinkler,
    COALESCE(R.RatingTerritory, 'Unknown Territory') AS rating_territory,
    COALESCE(R.RatingTerritoryDesc, 'Unknown Territory') AS rating_territory_desc,
    COALESCE(R.RiskAddress, 'Not Applicable') AS risk_address,
    COALESCE(R.RiskCity, 'Not Applicable') AS risk_city,
    COALESCE(R.RiskCounty, 'Not Applicable') AS risk_county,
    COALESCE(R.RiskPostalCd, 'Not Applicable') AS risk_zip,
    COALESCE(R.PersonalLiabilityLimit, 'Other') AS personal_umbrella_limit,
    COALESCE(R.BulidingNumber, 'Not Applicable') AS building_num,
    COALESCE(R.buildingstatus, 'Not Applicable') AS building_status,
    COALESCE(R.NumberOfApartmentsBand, 'Not Applicable') AS number_of_apartments_band,
    COALESCE(R.NumberOfApartmentsCondo, 'Not Applicable') AS total_num_of_units_in_complex,
    COALESCE(R.NumberOfStories, 'Unknown') AS number_of_stories,
    NULL AS number_of_stories_band,
    COALESCE(R.SqFeetArea, 'Not Applicable') AS sq_feet_area,
    COALESCE(R.SqFtAreaBand, 'Not Applicable') AS sq_feet_area_band,
    COALESCE(REPLACE(LTRIM(REPLACE(R.StandardDeductible, '0', ' ')), ' ', '0'), 'Unknown Policy Deductible') AS deductible,
    R.Num_Vehicles AS num_vehicles,
    R.DistanceToShoreBand AS distancetoshore_band,
    R.SIRCoastlineBand AS sircoastline_band,
    R.NumOfBuildingsComplex AS num_buildings_complex,
    R.BuildingClassDescription AS building_class_description,
    R.ContentsClassDescription AS contents_class_description,
	R.FormattedRiskAddress AS formatted_risk_address,
    R.FormattedRiskCity AS formatted_risk_city,
    R.FormattedRiskZipCode AS formatted_risk_zip,
    R.FormattedLatitude AS formatted_risk_latitude,
    R.FormattedLongitude AS formatted_risk_longitude,
	R.ElitePackageInd AS elite_package_ind,
	R.FormattedStreet AS formatted_street,
    R.FormattedCounty AS formatted_county,
	R."PremisesLiability" AS premises_liability,
	R."BuildingWindHailDeductible" AS wind_or_hail_deductible,
	R."DistanceToShore" AS distance_to_shore,
    "SIRCoastline" AS sir_coastline,
    "CyberLiabilityLimit" AS cyber_liability_limit,
    COALESCE("OnPremisesLimit", 0) + COALESCE("OffPremisesLimit", 0) AS money_and_securities,
    "ValuablePapersRecords" AS valuable_papers,
    "FoodSpoilageLimit" AS food_spoilage,
    "FungiProperty" AS limited_fungi_or_bacteria_coverage,
    COALESCE("DemolitionLimit", 0) + COALESCE("IncreasedCostConstructionLimit", 0) + COALESCE("CombDemolitionIncCostLimit", 0) AS ordinance_or_law,
    ExtBuildingBroadLimit AS extended_building_broad_form_water,
    ExtBuildingEQLimit AS extended_building_earthquake,
    ExtBuildingFloodLimit AS extended_building_flood,
    ExteriorSignsLimit AS exterior_signs,
    ISOEarthquakeLimit AS iso_earthquake,
    FireDistrict AS fire_district

FROM int_msgr.risk R
inner JOIN policyDetails P ON R."PolicyKey" = P."PolicyKey"
LEFT JOIN int_msgr.dim_construction_year Y ON "YearBuilt" BETWEEN Y."lo" AND Y."hi"
LEFT JOIN (select distinct GWOccupancyCd,Display_OccupancyDesc from int_msgr.occupancycd_ref) O ON O."GWOccupancyCd" = R."OccupancyCd"
 LEFT JOIN int_msgr.lkp_building_limit_band BL
ON CASE
       WHEN R."buildingstatus" <> 'Deleted' THEN CAST(R.BuildingLimit AS NUMERIC(8, 0))
       ELSE 0
   END >= BL."Limit_Value_Low"
AND CASE
       WHEN R."buildingstatus" <> 'Deleted' THEN CAST(R."BuildingLimit" AS NUMERIC(8, 0))
       ELSE 0
   END <= BL."Limit_Value_High"
LEFT JOIN int_msgr.dim_limits_new L ON  P.policy_parent_dim_id = L.ParentDimID AND  (BuildingLimit::numeric BETWEEN L.Lo AND L.Hi )
LEFT JOIN int_msgr.dim_limits_new DL ON P.policy_parent_dim_id = DL.ParentDimID  AND "ContentsLimit"::numeric BETWEEN DL."Lo" AND DL."Hi"
 AND P.policy_parent_dim_id = L."ParentDimID"

LEFT join (select risk_key,etl_insert_dt from cert_msgr.dim_risk where datasource_name='Guidewire') AS tg_dim_risk on R."RiskID"=tg_dim_risk.risk_key
where RowEffEndDt = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'

parameters.name: $SQ_pms_risk$
parameters.label: SQ_pms_risk
parameters.customQuery:
SELECT
'PMS' as datasource_name,
R.Risk_Id::VARCHAR(255) as risk_key,
R.Policy_Key_Code as policy_key_code,
CASE
    WHEN SUBSTRING(R.Policy_Key_Code FROM LENGTH(R.Policy_Key_Code)-3) = '-999'
        OR (
            SUBSTRING(R.Policy_Key_Code FROM 1 FOR 3) = 'SBP'
            AND SUBSTRING(R.Policy_Key_Code FROM LENGTH(R.Policy_Key_Code)-3) = '-000'
            )
    THEN 0
    ELSE 1
END AS
policy_key_code_flag,
P.blanket_policy_ind as blanket_policy_ind,
--COALESCE(R.form, 'Not Applicable') AS form,
COALESCE(R.Risk_State, 'Not Applicable') AS risk_state,
COALESCE(P.Secondary_Home_Desc, 'Not Applicable') as secondary_home_desc,
 R.coverage_a_premium AS cov_a_premium,
    R.coverage_c_premium AS cov_c_premium,
    COALESCE(R.building_limits_group, 'Not Applicable') AS building_limits_group,
    COALESCE(R.building_limits, 'Not Applicable') AS building_limits,
    R.Building_Amount AS building_limit_amt,
    COALESCE(R.building_limit_band_1k, 'Not Applicable') AS building_limit_band_1k,
    COALESCE(R.building_limit_band_100k, 'Not Applicable') AS building_limit_band_100k,
    COALESCE(R.building_limit_band_500k, 'Not Applicable') AS building_limit_band_500k,
    CAST(R.contents_amount AS NUMERIC(8, 0)) AS contents_limit,
    R.total_insured_value AS total_insured_value,
    COALESCE(CAST(R.individual_risk_premium_mod AS VARCHAR(120)), 'Not Applicable') AS individual_risk_premium_mod,
    COALESCE(CAST(R.expense_mod AS VARCHAR(120)), 'Not Applicable') AS expense_mod,
    COALESCE(CAST(R.age_credit AS VARCHAR(120)), 'Not Applicable') AS age_credit_amt,
    COALESCE(CAST(R.dupc AS VARCHAR(120)), 'Not Applicable') AS dupc_credit_amt,
    COALESCE(CAST(R.prc AS VARCHAR(100)), 'Not Applicable') AS prc_credit,
    R.latitude AS latitude
    ,R.longitude AS longitude,
    'Wind/Hail/Hurricane PMS' AS wind_deductible_type,
    R.wind_site_deductible AS wind_deductible_amt,
    R.per_unit_deductible_type AS per_unit_deductible_type,
    R.per_unit_deductible_amt AS per_unit_deductible_amt,
    R.distance_to_coast_feet AS distance_to_shore_feet,
    R.distance_to_coast_mile AS distance_to_shore_mile,
    R.sir_result_feet AS sir_coastline_feet,
    R.sir_mile::VARCHAR(100) AS sir_coastline_mile,
COALESCE(R.flood, 'Not Applicable') AS flood_zone,
COALESCE( R.elevation, 'Not Applicable') AS elevation,
    COALESCE(R.Building_Class_Code,R.Contents_Class_Code,  'Not Applicable') AS class_code,
    CASE
        WHEN R.Building_Class_Code IS NULL OR R.Building_Class_Code = 'Not Applicable' THEN  R.Contents_Class_Code
        ELSE R.Building_Class_Code
    END AS building_class_code,
    CASE
        WHEN R.Contents_Class_Code IS NULL OR R.Contents_Class_Code = 'Not Applicable' THEN '65121'
        ELSE R.Contents_Class_Code
    END AS contents_class_code,
    COALESCE(R.construction_type, 'Unknown Construction Type') AS construction_type,
    COALESCE(NULLIF(R.construction_year, ''), 'Unknown Construction Year') AS construction_year,
    COALESCE(R.construction_year_band, 'Unknown Construction Year') AS construction_year_band,
    COALESCE(R.contents_limits, 'Unknown Limit') AS contents_limits_group,
    COALESCE(R.contents_limits, 'Unknown Limit') AS contents_limits,
--    'Other' AS coverage_desc,
   COALESCE(R.liability_limit, 'Other') AS liability_limit,
    CAST(
    (COALESCE(R.commercial_umbrella_liability_limit, 0)
    + COALESCE(R.commercial_excess_liability_limit, 0))
AS VARCHAR) AS commercial_liability_limit,
    R.water_backup_limit AS water_backup_limit,
    CASE
    WHEN LEN(R.number_of_apartments) <= 2 THEN RIGHT('000' + R.number_of_apartments, 3)
    WHEN R.number_of_apartments IS NULL OR R.number_of_apartments = '' THEN 'Unknown Number of Apartments'
    ELSE R.number_of_apartments
END AS number_of_apartments,
    COALESCE(R.number_of_families, 'Other') AS number_of_families,
    COALESCE(R.Display_OccupancyDesc, 'Not Applicable') AS occupancy,
    COALESCE(R.protection_class, 'Not Applicable') AS protection_class,
    CASE
    WHEN R.sprinkler_indicator = 'No' THEN 'None'
    WHEN R.sprinkler_indicator is NULL THEN 'Not Applicable'
    ELSE R.sprinkler_indicator
END AS sprinkler,
    COALESCE(R.rating_territory, 'Unknown Territory') AS rating_territory,
    COALESCE(R.rating_territory_desc, 'Unknown Territory') AS rating_territory_desc,
COALESCE(
    NULLIF(
        TRIM(
            COALESCE(R.Risk_Address_Line_1, '')
            || ' '
            || COALESCE(R.Risk_Address_Line_2, '')
            || ' '
            || COALESCE(R.Risk_Address_Line_3, '')
        ),
    ''),
    'Not Applicable'
) AS risk_address,
    COALESCE(R.risk_city, 'Not Applicable') AS risk_city,
    COALESCE(RS.dim_desc, 'Not Applicable') AS risk_county,
    COALESCE(R.Risk_Postal_Cd, 'Not Applicable') AS risk_zip,
    COALESCE(R.personal_umbrella_limit, 'Other') AS personal_umbrella_limit,
    RIGHT(R.policy_key_code, 3) AS building_num,
    'Not Applicable' AS building_status,
    COALESCE(R.number_of_apartments_band, 'Not Applicable') AS number_of_apartments_band,
    'Not Applicable' AS total_num_of_units_in_complex,
    COALESCE(NULLIF(R.number_of_stories, ''), 'Unknown') AS number_of_stories,
    COALESCE(NULLIF(R.number_of_stories_band, ''), 'Unknown') AS number_of_stories_band,
    COALESCE(R.sq_feet_area, 'Not Applicable') AS sq_feet_area,
    COALESCE(R.sqft_area_band, 'Not Applicable') AS sq_feet_area_band,
    CASE
        WHEN R.deductible <> 'Unknown Policy Deductible' THEN LTRIM(RTRIM(REPLACE(R.deductible, '0', ' ')))
        ELSE R.deductible
    END AS deductible,
    R.num_vehicles,
    R.Distance_To_ShoreBand AS distance_to_shore_band,
    R.sir_coastline_band AS sir_coastline_band,
    R.risk_count::integer as num_buildings_complex,
    CASE
        WHEN LEFT(R.policy_key_code, 3) = 'SBP' AND (R.Building_Class_Code IS NULL OR R.Building_Class_Code = 'Not Applicable') THEN 'None - Contents Coverage Only'
        ELSE R.building_class_description
    END AS building_class_description,
    CASE
        WHEN LEFT(R.policy_key_code, 3) = 'SBP' AND (R.Contents_Class_Code IS NULL OR R.Contents_Class_Code = 'Not Applicable') THEN 'None - Building Owner Only'
        ELSE R.contents_class_description
    END AS contents_class_description,
         R.FormattedRiskAddress as formatted_risk_address,
             R.FormattedRiskCity as formatted_risk_city,
    R.FormattedRiskZipCode as formatted_risk_zip,
    R.FormattedLatitude as formatted_risk_latitude,
    R.FormattedLongitude as formatted_risk_longitude,
    'Not Applicable' AS elite_package_ind,
    R.FormattedStreet as formatted_street,
    R.FormattedCounty as formatted_county,
	null as premises_liability,
	null as wind_or_hail_deductible,
	R.distance_To_Coast AS distance_to_shore,
	Sir_Coastline_Band as sir_coastline,
	R.Cyber_Liability_Limit ::VARCHAR(255) AS cyber_liability_limit,
	COALESCE(R.OnPremises_Limit, 0) + COALESCE(R.OffPremises_Limit, 0) AS money_and_securities,
	R.Valuable_Papers_Limit::VARCHAR(255) AS valuable_papers,
	R.Food_Spoilage_Limit as food_spoilage,
	R.Fungi_Property_Limit::VARCHAR(255) AS limited_fungi_or_bacteria_coverage,
	COALESCE(R."Demolition_Limit", 0) + COALESCE(R."Increased_Cost_Construction_Limit", 0) + COALESCE(R."Combined_Demolition_Increased_Cost_Limit", 0) AS ordinance_or_law,
	R.Ext_Building_Broad_Limit AS extended_building_broad_form_water,
    R.Ext_Building_EQ_Limit AS extended_building_earthquake,
    R."Ext_Building_Flood_Limit" AS extended_building_flood,
    R."Exterior_Signs_Limit" AS exterior_signs,
    R."ISO_EQ_Limit" AS iso_earthquake,
    R."Fire_District" AS fire_district
FROM int_msgr.pms_master_risk_hist R
left join (select distinct row_start_dt ,policy_key, blanket_policy_ind  ,Secondary_Home_Desc,Risk_State
from int_msgr.pms_master_policy_hist P where  P.Row_End_Dt = '9999-12-31') P on P.policy_key=R.policy_key
left join int_msgr.HIER_dim_RiskState RS on RS.dim_id=P.Risk_State
LEFT join (select risk_key,etl_insert_dt from cert_msgr.dim_risk where datasource_name='PMS') AS tg_dim_risk on R.risk_id=tg_dim_risk.risk_key
where R. Row_eff_End_Dt = '9999-12-31'
